data.description: New roof in 2021 and the exterior was just painted this summer! Fantastic home on a spacious lot with an open floor plan, tall ceilings, hardwood floors, fireplace and lots of windows for natural light. This home has 4 bedrooms, a living room AND a family room PLUS an office!! This kitchen has quartz counters, SS appliances, a gas range & a pantry. The primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings, a large walk in closet, double single vanities and a tiled shower. You will love the private backyard with a deck and shed! Close to I5/205, shops/Legacy. Great schools!
